lead_paragraph: When Serena Williams plays as well as she did in the semifinals of the Australian Open, there's little an opponent can do to challenge her. Even one who's soon to be ranked No. 3 in the world, just two places behind her.

headline.print_headline: Williams Reaches 7th Australian Open Final in Dominant Form
